1: get request means client ko data chahiye
2: post menas server py data upload krna hy
    best way to hanle post request is to install postman
    download the postman
    postman helps to post request
    body ko read krny k lconfiguration krni pry gi is k liye req aa rhi hy to beech mn koi aesa hona chaiye jo req ki body mn json bhja hy usy object mn convert kry java script k or req ki .body property set kr dy
    is k liye middleware use krty hyn
    middleware jo request aa rhi hy us sy wo json ko read kry ga or request.body naam ki jo property jo ho gi us k under us ko onject bana k save kr dy ga or usy bd  mn hm use kryn gy   

3: put : is request mn data ko update krty hyn.
        jb url likh k postman py serach kiya to id 1 mill gya mtlb read kr li id server py
        ab is k bd search krna hy then data update krna hy.
        data send ho ga body k sath postman mn

4: delete: is request mn data ko delete krty hyn.
